UNITED STATES of America, Appellant, v. CHIN LIN SHEE, alias Chin Yau Hop, Appellee. Jan. 21, 1932. Circuit Court of Appeals, Ninth Circuit.

Before WILBUR and SAWTELLE, Circuit Judges, and McCORMICK, District Judge.

PER CURIAM.

Pursuant to motion of appellant, ordered appeal dismissed; mandate forthwith;
